  "texts": [
    "They comprise potent modelling approaches that recognize intricate patterns in vast volumes of data (Ferentinos 2018).",
    "Studies that don't have enough data for neural networks to operate can nevertheless add data.",
    "CNNs replaced the earlier ANNs.",
    "ANNs were created for domains with recurring patterns, such as identifying unhealthy plant images.",
    "Numerous algorithms have been effectively employed to categorize plant diseases using CNNs, making crop health monitoring simpler."
